<Defs>
	<ThingDef Name="RobCo_ProtectronCivilianBlasterBase" ParentName="RobCo_BaseGun" Abstract="True"><label>RobCo Civilian Blaster</label><description>A pre-War RobCo sidearm intended for civilian security and general self-defense. It uses a low-beam laser cartridge and is less powerful than RobCo's military models.</description><statBases><MarketValue>500</MarketValue><Mass>2</Mass><AccuracyTouch>0.70</AccuracyTouch><AccuracyShort>0.65</AccuracyShort><AccuracyMedium>0.50</AccuracyMedium><AccuracyLong>0.30</AccuracyLong><RangedWeapon_Cooldown>2.0</RangedWeapon_Cooldown></statBases><verbs><li><verbClass>Verb_Shoot</verbClass><range>20</range><warmupTime>0.4</warmupTime><defaultProjectile>RobCo_Bullet_LaserLow</defaultProjectile><burstShotCount>1</burstShotCount></li></verbs></ThingDef>
	<ThingDef Name="RobCo_ProtectronMilitaryBlasterBase" ParentName="RobCo_BaseGun" Abstract="True"><label>RobCo Military Blaster</label><description>A RobCo service blaster designed for military and security use. It fires high-beam laser cartridges that provide more stopping power than the civilian pattern.</description><statBases><MarketValue>1200</MarketValue><Mass>3.5</Mass><AccuracyTouch>0.80</AccuracyTouch><AccuracyShort>0.70</AccuracyShort><AccuracyMedium>0.55</AccuracyMedium><AccuracyLong>0.40</AccuracyLong><RangedWeapon_Cooldown>2.5</RangedWeapon_Cooldown></statBases><verbs><li><verbClass>Verb_Shoot</verbClass><range>22</range><warmupTime>0.6</warmupTime><defaultProjectile>RobCo_Bullet_LaserHigh</defaultProjectile><burstShotCount>1</burstShotCount></li></verbs></ThingDef>
